OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAngelina Jolie steps down  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fas UN refugee envoy        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Oscar-winning US actress Angelina Jolie
OL,6, says she is stepping down from her role
OL,7, as an ambassador for the UN refugee    
OL,8, agency UNHCR after more than 20 years. 
OL,10,F"I believe in many things the UN does, 
OL,11,Fparticularly the lives it saves through
OL,12,Femergency relief," Jolie, 47, said.    
OL,14,FAnd she added: "I will be working now  
OL,15,Fwith organisations led by people most  
OL,16,Fdirectly affected by conflict, that    
OL,17,Fgive the greatest voice to them."      
OL,19,FThe UNHCR said she was one of the most 
OL,20,Finfluential refugee rights advocates.  
